{"tid":2379754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子挾持中學生  稱死前想要殺警察","createTime":"2021-01-25T12:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T12:22:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72336cf439b30a69aa1e981861298ef6a32d0132","tid":2379754,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.soundofhope.org/2021-01/students-5201691_640-1611572624053.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.soundofhope.org%2F2021-01%2Fstudents-5201691_640-1611572624053.jpg&h=a27a8c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子在學校門口傷人並劫持人質（圖片來源：視頻截圖）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/467444?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F467444%3Flang%3Db5&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=74fbb4a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/467444?lang=b5</a>"},{"pid":"1cb52102ac499081d4b7cfaa846077561896885a","tid":2379754,"uid":203889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:10:35.000Z","msg":"希望之聲2021年1月25日】（本台記者楚雲珒綜合報導）近日，位於雲南昆明的雲南師範大學實驗中學門口發生一起劫持人質事件，造成1死7傷。據之前網絡流傳的視頻顯示，該男子用刀指着一名學生的脖子，用揚聲器向周圍的羣衆和警察喊話，稱自己父母都在中共文革時捱過批鬥，自己吸過毒但社會不給改正的機會。他還稱，&ldquo;想要殺警察，只是殺一個......中國人的生命就像螻蟻一樣，被貪官污吏踩在腳下&rdquo;。這段視頻上傳至網絡立刻引發大量關注，但隨後被刪的無影無蹤。"},{"pid":"01b8409ce04d7e382bdc410a5703e5e321b1a8d5","tid":2379754,"uid":68375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"條友臨尾比sniper 爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07548b9a02b99ed289be2a5064820a66550d97bf","tid":2379754,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"蝦啲中學雞托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a914101660e02e1eda906c7edabf2c427309caa1","tid":2379754,"uid":166313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b8409ce04d7e382bdc410a5703e5e321